data.description: This naturally beautiful single story well kept home, none smokers, has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage and an office. Spacious island kitchen, stainless steel sink. Stainless steel appliances, stove/oven, microwave, refrigerator, water softener connection, nice dining room area, walk-in pantry, w/washer/dryer connections. Spacious primary bedroom and spacious living room with ceiling fans. Neighborhood pool, park, Sand Volleyball, basketball court. Conveniently located minutes to La Cantera Shops, the Rim, fine dining and entertainment, theater, HEB PLUS, UTSA, Fiesta Texas, Sea World, NISD school district, and quick access to 1604.
